TITLE: Configure package exports for monorepo TypeScript development
DESCRIPTION: This JSON snippet shows how to configure the `exports` field in a `package.json` file to support direct referencing of TypeScript source files in a monorepo. The `typescript` condition allows Node.js to load `.ts` files directly, streamlining development by avoiding rebuilds of internal packages.

SOURCE: https://github.com/nodejs/node/blob/main/deps/amaro/README.md#_snippet_4

